# cdinsights Component
This component showcases a section of "Insights and Perspectives" that can list multiple "items" each with a title, subtitle, and image. The default variant uses a flex layout with images, while the demo variant uses placeholder data from the `demoVariantData.ts`.

## Key Features
- `heading` and `tagline` define the main text
- `items` array can contain multiple sub-entries

## Notes
1. We based it on the reference from [hero] and [__[template] examples in the default theme.
2. We implemented both a default variant and a demo variant (xDemo).
3. The sample images and text data in the default variant references `matchingData`.
4. There's an array of items to show multiple posts/insights in a grid or flex layout.